				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "It's another debtor that players can meet in Feast Hall. \r\nHe is the reference to a character that was mentioned in Act 2, Mason\r\n\r\nCurrently he's placed in the Feast Hall (as it will only win from adding another character), and it makes sense for him to clean the surrounding mess."
